## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited number of sources, which may not capture the full diversity of perspectives on attachment theory in education. Additionally, the search was restricted to English-language sources, potentially excluding relevant research published in other languages. The lack of specific publication dates for some sources may also affect the currency and relevance of the information provided.